, \"value\": 0.45, \"unit\": \"0-1\", \"note\": \"Medium-low: evidence relies partly on aggregator pages; official SSE list not successfully extracted; limited confirmation of any very fresh (Feb-28/Mar-1) material event.\"}], \"confidence\": 0.42}, {\"factor_id\": \"factor.common.market_calendar_and_trading_status_guard_sse.guard\", \"evidence\": [\"SSE announcement (上交所公告〔2025〕45号), 2025-12-22: published 2026 holiday/closure arrangements; no March closures listed (https://www.sse.com.cn/disclosure/announcement/general/c/c_20251222_10802507.shtml).\", \"SSE '2026年年度休市安排' page: lists 2026 closures (Jan 1-3, Feb 15-23, Apr 4-6, May 1-5, Jun 19-21, Sep 25-27, Oct 1-7); March 2026 not listed as closed (https://www.sse.com.cn/disclosure/dealinstruc/closed/).\", \"SSE English trading schedule page: confirms normal trading hours structure (opening call auction, continuous auction, closing call auction 14:57-15:00), supporting normal-session definition (https://english.sse.com.cn/start/trading/schedule/; accessed 2026-03-01 context).\", \"SSE-site search results for '605117 停牌' primarily return historical (2021) intraday volatility halts; no clear evidence surfaced for a 2025/2026 suspension, but this is not authoritative confirmation of current tradability (google search results pointing to SSE disclosures; queried 2026-03-01).\"], \"signals\": [{\"name\": \"is_trading_day_ok\", \"value\": true, \"unit\": null, \"note\": \"2026 SSE closure schedule (official) shows no holiday/closure on 2026-03-02; Monday trading expected.\"}, {\"name\": \"is_tradable_ok\", \"value\": false, \"unit\": null, \"note\": \"Fail-closed due to missing authoritative as-of-2026-03-01 confirmation of no suspension/halt/ST status for 605117.SH on/into 2026-03-02.\"}, {\"name\": \"is_normal_session_ok\", \"value\": true, \"unit\": null, \"note\": \"No evidence of market-wide special/shortened session for 2026-03-02 found; SSE standard hours apply.\"}], \"confidence\": 0.48}]\n\n\nReturn a structured